# Auto-Anvil

# Obtaining

The auto anvil is one of the more complicated crafting recipes. You can find it under the category "Energy & Electricity" on the second page.

# Tiers

There are 2 tiers of this machine. Tier 1 has a Repair Factor of 10%, Tier2 20%.

# Usage

Place the item you want to repair together with "Duct Tape" in the machine and wait. (You need energy for it to work)
